Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.21,0:02:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.75,0:02:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...head for the New World,\Nthe second half of the Grand Line.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.93,0:03:07.31,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, no one has ever fully explored it\Nexcept for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.31,0:03:13.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The New World has ruined\Nmany pirates' dreams and ambitions.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.36,0:03:17.49,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.49,0:03:20.54,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,to rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.54,0:03:22.91,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and his friends venture into that sea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.99,0:03:26.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.08,0:03:32.37,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and the others left Dressrosa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.37,0:03:34.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and are heading for their \Nnext destination, Zou,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.99,0:03:38.32,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,to meet up with the other half of their crew.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.34,0:03:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, they were attacked by Battle Boats\Nout of the blue{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.92,0:03:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and Luffy was taken to an unknown island, \NSilver Mine along with Bartolomeo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.64,0:03:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His life was put in danger by Bill who is \Nthe leader of the Silver Pirate Alliance,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.94,0:03:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and then, fell into an underground mineshaft\Nwhere he learned the truth about Bill.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.78,0:04:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!\NHe wouldn't do such a thing to his friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.24,0:04:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's hard to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.32,0:04:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.70,0:04:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Did Bill really tell you to...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.00,0:04:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...get rid of me as well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.46,0:04:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.09,0:04:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.50,0:04:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.30,0:04:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Jet Bazooka!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.11,0:04:38.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,AVELON EXPRESS
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.23,0:04:40.82,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,TERMINAL STATION
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.94,0:04:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fought in collaboration with Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0}\Nfor the first time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.37,0:04:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Straw Hat and the others make \Nit up here, we'll be in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.51,0:05:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, let's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.99,0:05:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...bury them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.64,0:05:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"The Sword Technique Heats Up!\NLaw and Zoro Finally Appear!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.90,0:05:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the railroad?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.44,0:05:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that one goes highest.\NThey were using it to carry ore out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.86,0:05:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we don't know what lies ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.53,0:05:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we gotta leave the rest to chance,\Nright, Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.04,0:05:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.88,0:05:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.96,0:05:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm so thrilled!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.30,0:05:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By responding to his commands,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.89,0:05:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I'm a member of the Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.39,0:05:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?! You guys aren't up for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.35,0:06:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we do wanna get out of here but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.77,0:06:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Bill finds us,\Nwe'll be taken back here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.49,0:06:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition, we'll receive \Nterrible punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.40,0:06:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys afraid of?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.57,0:06:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0} has the power \Nof a hundred people!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, a thousand or 10 thousand or 100 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.91,0:06:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.27,0:06:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no matter how strong he is,\Nhe is no match for Bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.84,0:06:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna have molten metal poured on me\Nand be turned into a statue!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.64,0:06:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, besides Bill,\Nthey have a scary executive called Peseta.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.22,0:06:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pffft! Do as you like, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.10,0:06:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.94,0:06:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've made up my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.10,0:06:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna get out of here with \NStraw Hat to go settle things!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.86,0:06:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go settle things?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.73,0:06:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you guys wanna spend\Nthe rest of your lives here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.99,0:06:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you stay here,\Nyou can't do anything but wait to be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.91,0:06:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If so, isn't it better to take your chances\Nand try to get off of the island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.41,0:07:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show some guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.83,0:07:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you say you're still a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.92,0:07:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.09,0:07:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.51,0:07:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna go along with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.14,0:07:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.94,0:07:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.19,0:07:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job making it this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.21,0:07:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.51,0:07:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.43,0:07:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.28,0:08:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm landing on Luffy-senpai's \NGum-Gum Balloon...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.36,0:08:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a blissful moment!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.58,0:08:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you sleeping?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.25,0:08:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out! The overpass is collapsing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.63,0:08:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me handle it! Barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.73,0:08:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, Crest Head!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.52,0:08:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks! I'm honored I could \Nbe of some help to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.86,0:08:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.30,0:09:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really incredible! \NIncredible! Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.66,0:09:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peseta! Are these Bill's orders again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.17,0:09:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.29,0:09:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gonna bury these guys alive as well\Nafter driving them so hard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.01,0:09:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trying to spare just them is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.78,0:09:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...incredibly troublesome! So I'll just...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.64,0:09:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...take care of them along with you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.37,0:09:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That makes me angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.87,0:09:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Barrier Crush!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.03,0:09:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is a dangerous barrier as they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.12,0:09:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.70,0:09:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Barrier-bility!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.64,0:09:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.14,0:10:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! The stairs made of the barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.23,0:10:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and climb them, Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.69,0:10:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you looking the other way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.46,0:10:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Crest Head, I'll go first!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.49,0:10:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.24,0:10:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I mean, I'll come with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.53,0:10:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is awesome! I'm having so much fun!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.87,0:10:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm correct, there is \Na limit on the size of
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.84,0:10:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the barrier that you can produce at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.64,0:10:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.43,0:10:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used it up on the staircase!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.48,0:10:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.55,0:10:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Climb all the way up quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.53,0:11:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.87,0:11:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peseta-{\i1}sama{\i0}! We gotta do something or...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.89,0:11:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't panic!\NI already have plan B and C ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.81,0:11:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll burn you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.36,0:11:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shambles!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.41,0:11:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me! Foxfire Style!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.16,0:11:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire-Willow Flash!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.16,0:11:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.61,0:11:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kin'emon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.46,0:11:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no fire that I can't cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.26,0:12:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.27,0:12:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.82,0:12:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.78,0:12:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Elephant Gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.87,0:12:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally made it above ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.92,0:12:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0}'s Elephant Gun!\NI got to see such a great thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.43,0:12:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you just standing?\NLet's go already!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.53,0:12:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, you can't go any farther!\NDon't think you won!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.10,0:12:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you again, {\i1}Penta{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.96,0:12:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's {\i1}Peseta{\i0}! Take a look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.61,0:13:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.15,0:13:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sis Desire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.03,0:13:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you resist, they'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.30,0:13:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I need you to come \Nalong without fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.49,0:13:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How cunning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.16,0:13:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peseta! You're really terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.71,0:13:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Terrible? I don't think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.07,0:13:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean incredible, don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.06,0:13:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.52,0:13:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.82,0:13:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.32,0:14:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.16,0:14:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When his friends have their \Nback against the wall,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.52,0:14:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he appears at the right moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.97,0:14:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro-{\i1}senpai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.20,0:14:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, I have to pay him back. Let me do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.95,0:14:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.00,0:14:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you be so composed,\NPirate Hunter Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.38,0:14:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a bounty of 320 million
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.47,0:14:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you were pretty \Npathetic when we last met!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.26,0:14:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laugh at him! Just laugh at him, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.94,0:15:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard!\NHow dare he make fun of Zoro-{\i1}senpai{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.94,0:15:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna beat the hell out of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.53,0:15:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.41,0:15:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.25,0:15:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know your place!\NI'll immobilize you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.27,0:15:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One-Sword Style iai...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.11,0:15:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! My Adhesive Shell should\Nstick to anything that it touches!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.08,0:15:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be shameful for a swordsman\Nto even let that disgusting
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,thing touch his blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.07,0:16:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only Zoro-{\i1}dono{\i0} could've done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.58,0:16:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.15,0:16:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro-{\i1}senpai{\i0} sliced up all the Adhesive Shells\Nwith just one single slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.13,0:16:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's far from over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.22,0:16:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.14,0:16:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.01,0:16:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.23,0:16:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There! There! There! There!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.07,0:16:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three-Sword Style...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.36,0:16:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Black Rope Dragon Twister!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.66,0:16:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did that twister come from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.34,0:16:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.01,0:16:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.09,0:16:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's terrible!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.80,0:16:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.31,0:16:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, now is our chance!\NTake everybody to the port!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.40,0:17:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll leave the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.98,0:17:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! But what are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.86,0:17:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come after I settle things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.14,0:17:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, we'll come with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.83,0:17:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a problem of my own making.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.25,0:17:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me do it on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.26,0:17:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Promise us you'll come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.47,0:17:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't leave until you come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.10,0:17:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.98,0:17:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let's go, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.03,0:17:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys saved our lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.86,0:17:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.36,0:17:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.58,0:18:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wanna settle things with Bill?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's none of your business.\N--Do you still believe in that jerk?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.33,0:18:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's quite the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.91,0:18:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let me settle something \Nwith you, Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.44,0:18:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.18,0:18:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize to you for my rudeness till now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.39,0:18:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.01,0:18:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind! The chocolate \Nyou gave me was delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.90,0:18:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go! Usopp and the others \Nare waiting at the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.28,0:18:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, it's only a matter of time \Nbefore enemy boats attack us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.89,0:18:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must hurry up too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.28,0:18:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.84,0:18:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch! Ouch! Ouch! Ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.55,0:19:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.10,0:19:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.68,0:19:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sum total of Straw Hat and Pirate \NHunter's bounties is 820 million
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.73,0:19:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it was my chance to \Ncapture them both at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.65,0:19:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bill!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.28,0:19:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Luffy!\N--We'll back you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.78,0:19:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, just go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.12,0:19:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.29,0:19:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of Usopp and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.62,0:19:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.58,0:19:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.80,0:19:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about Pirate Hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.63,0:19:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not gonna let a man with \Na bounty of 500 million get away,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.38,0:19:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.21,0:20:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! Franky-{\i1}senpai{\i0} has taken the trouble to\Nrepair this Mister Luffy Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.92,0:20:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let them damage it any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.76,0:20:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.45,0:20:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Special Attack: Green Star - Sea Devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.38,0:20:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dodge!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.46,0:20:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weapon's Left!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.99,0:20:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mil Fleurs...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.89,0:20:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Gigantesco Mano!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.68,0:20:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They keep coming, one after another!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.11,0:20:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Isn't Straw Hat-{\i1}ya{\i0} here yet?\N--I guess he's having trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.07,0:20:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.58,0:20:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.31,0:20:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who must settle things with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.60,0:20:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmmm, "settle things"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.46,0:21:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My way of settling things is\Nto collect all the bounties!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.84,0:21:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna smelt you along \Nwith this mine for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.28,0:21:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!\NIf you do that, your subordinates will...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.01,0:21:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.64,0:21:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their bounties are so low\Ncompared to Straw Hat and the others
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.44,0:21:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's better than nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.56,0:21:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to make my dream come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.32,0:21:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your dream is\Nto dominate the Pirate Era, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.30,0:21:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you told me when \Nyou saved me, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.21,0:21:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saved you? Yeah, I did save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.64,0:21:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you had the capability \Nto lead a girl gang,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.29,0:21:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I could use you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.68,0:21:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.35,0:22:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you were the one \Nwho sank our boats that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.45,0:22:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.12,0:22:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.66,0:22:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sank them and saved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.67,0:22:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I perform as good as a stage actor?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.39,0:22:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And guess what?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.30,0:22:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The simple minded idiot \Nthat you are got wrapped up
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.15,0:22:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in my dream like a loyal dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.43,0:22:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what this is all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.44,0:22:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.82,0:22:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's unforgivable...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.67,0:22:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.58,0:23:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...take advantage of our compassion!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.01,0:23:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your tears are pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.90,0:23:28.22,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Guild Tesoro, the golden \Nemperor behind the curtain,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.22,0:23:30.60,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,brings out Bill's hidden ability!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.60,0:23:33.62,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When Luffy's angry fist clashes with Bill
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.62,0:23:36.00,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,who rages out of control in blazing fire,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.00,0:23:40.06,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the battle in Silver Mine \Nfinally comes to a climax!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.08,0:23:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.44,0:23:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Desperate Situation! Luffy \NFights a Battle in Extreme Heat!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.02,0:23:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.05,0:23:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.05,0:23:52.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,
